            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "Finally, A Supplement That Actually Works",
            "text": "<p>\"I’ve tried several turmeric supplements, and this is the only one where I actually felt a difference. My knees used to ache getting out of bed—now I barely notice it. Highly recommend!\"</p>",
