            "title": "Doctor suggested it, and I’m glad I listened",
            "text": "<p>“I’ve tried a few different options, but this one really stands out. The ingredients feel clean and I can tell it’s carefully made. I’ve noticed a big improvement in how I feel overall—definitely a product I’ll keep using.”</p>",
