            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "Stopped taking ibuprofen after 2 weeks",
            "text": "<p>\"After 2 weeks, I noticed less stiffness and more energy. I even stopped taking ibuprofen daily. This has been a game changer for me.\"</p>",
