            "stars_rating": 5,
            "title": "Doctor Recommended. Science Backed.",
            "text": "<p>“As a healthcare professional, I’m impressed with the quality standards of this brand. The formulations are clean, thoughtfully dosed, and supported by strong nutritional science. I recommend these supplements for patients looking for safe, effective daily support.”</p>",
